{"tid":1553533,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"全 城 投 選 2 0 2 0 年 度 最 佳 機 場 ： 香 港 國 際 機 場","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:11:34.000Z","uid":42250,"like":216,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"7e32c7f2a26a4de062e01602d21ab7a779d16920","tid":1553533,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.worldairportsurvey.com/Surveys/favorite_airport.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldairportsurvey.com%2FSurveys%2Ffavorite_airport.html&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=6ba7979e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.worldairportsurvey.com/Surveys/favorite_airport.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場開業廿年一直都係世界十大機場<br />\n全賴咁多個遊客做呢份問卷<br />\n你首先要輸份機場名稱  Hong Kong International Airport, 之後就住50個範疇比分一至五粒星<br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場拎滿分50星就全靠大家<br />\n否則香港跌出十大, 機管局高層唔高興就慘"},{"pid":"7f4a765b179d58d286ae281de3cf3b9a0723003e","tid":1553533,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc2baffd70c29b6111e942b58a506661a96d864","tid":1553533,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bacd2cf5a313aa895a517aa2c2bebae04c36998","tid":1553533,"uid":42250,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"打漏左隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿分係250粒星先岩<br />\n打小左隻字, 50粒星係最低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAdmin唔該